---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Shajan Jacob
description: "Software Engineer | Hacker"
---

<section class="mb-8">
    <div class="leading-relaxed text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300 text-justify space-y-2">
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>I'm Shajan, a software engineer specializing in web applications development. I focus on building clean, reliable solutions while continuously exploring and experimenting with new ideas.</p>
        <p>When I'm not coding, I like tinkering with IoT and electronics—anything with wires or blinking lights instantly grabs my attention. I enjoy thoughtful design and creativity, whether it's selecting the right font color, making handmade crafts, or filling my space with plants. I also like capturing subtle moments through photography.</p>
        <p>I've worked with teams at Sorice, Cubet and other startups, helping build products with care and curiosity. I love what I do and enjoy working with people who want to create meaningful things.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Projects Section -->
<section class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline mb-6">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600">Projects</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        {% for project in collections.projects | reverse | batch(4) | first %}
        <article class="border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 p-4 rounded-sm flex flex-col justify-between">
            <div>
                <a href="{{ project.url }}" class="group flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
                    <h3 class="font-medium decoration-zinc-400 group-hover:text-zinc-600 dark:group-hover:text-zinc-300 transition-colors">{{ project.data.title }}</h3>
                </a>
                <p class="text-sm text-justify text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400">{{ project.data.description }}</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4">
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 mb-2">
                    {% for tag in project.data.tags %}
                    {% if tag != "projects" %}
                    <a href="/projects/tag/{{ tag }}/" class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wide px-1 py-0.5 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-500 rounded-sm hover:border-zinc-900 dark:hover:border-zinc-100 hover:text-zinc-900 dark:hover:text-zinc-100 transition-all duration-300">{{ tag }}</a>
                    {% endif %}
                    {% endfor %}
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                    <span class="text-xs text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600">{{ project.date | humanDate }}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/projects/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600 hover:text-zinc-900 dark:hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors group">
            See more projects<span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline mb-6">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600">Blog</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-4">
        {% for post in collections.blog | reverse | batch(4) | first %}
        <article class="mt-6">
            <a class="mt-4" href="{{ post.url }}" class="group block">
                <h3 class="font-medium group-hover:underline decoration-zinc-400 underline-offset-4">{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
            </a>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-justify text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
            <div class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
                {% if tag != "posts" and tag != "blog" %}
                <a href="/blog/tag/{{ tag }}/" class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wide px-1.5 py-0.5 border border-zinc-300 dark:border-zinc-700 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 rounded-sm hover:border-zinc-900 dark:hover:border-zinc-100 hover:text-zinc-900 dark:hover:text-zinc-100 transition-all duration-300">{{ tag }}</a>
                {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
            <span class="mt-2 text-xs text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600">{{ post.date | humanDate }}</span>
        </article>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/blog/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600 hover:text-zinc-900 dark:hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors group">
            See more blogs<span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
    </div>
</section>


<section class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline mb-6">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600">Photography</h2>
    </div>
    {% set photos = collections.photos | reverse | batch(4) | first %}
    {% include "components/photo-grid.njk" %}
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/photography/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600 hover:text-zinc-900 dark:hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors group">
            See more photos<span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
    </div>
</section>
